name: Innies: Better vulva
description:
Let's face it...

Stable diffusion can generate some... 'interesting' lady bits (horrors).

Perhaps the best alternative is to just generate less of it. Luckily, god gave us innies.

Add this lora to your text prompt, toy with the weights, get innies.

Check out my other LORA for shapely breast:

https://civitai.com/models/9025

Installation:

  1. Download the file

  2. Place it in models\Lora folder (webui)

Usage:

  1. Add the LORA to your text prompt. ex <lora:inniesBetterVulvas_v11:1.0>

  2. Adjust the weights. 0.1 - 1.0

Tips:

  • Not as aggressive as better bodies - values can be up to 0.9 before things get weird.

  • Helps to use text prompts like "thigh", "naked", etc.

  • Also pretty good at drawing models from behind, use prompts like "showing ass", "from behind", etc.

  • Skews towards the (adult) model's breast shape, so it might help to add in other breast types into your text prompt.

modelVersions.name: v1.1
modelVersions.description:
Should have less artifacts compared to the original:

  • Removed images with shadows - it was sampling them, causing weird hairs and lines on images that drove me insane debugging

  • Removed the one picture with straps - it caused a tendency towards drawing straps...

  • Removed pubic hair from model, draw your own (or don't)
